 5:47:17 PM\"><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">01-Jul-17</span></span></span></p>\n\n<p><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\"><strong>Requirements:</strong></span></span></span></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Female</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Minimum Bachelor Degree majoring in Early Childhood (S.Pd title)</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Maximum 40 years old</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Able to speak English both speaking &amp; writing</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Minimum 2 years teaching in Kindergarten 1 or Kindergarten 2</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Having experience with Montessori curriculum is an advantage</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Good communication skills</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">With passion and patient in kids</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Open to new methodology of teaching aside from conventional</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">With good moral characters and excellent interpersonal skills</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Having cheerful, lively &amp; energetic personality</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Talent in singing, dancing &amp; art are advantage</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Hardworking, adaptable, multi-tasking and flexible in time</span></span></span></li>\n	<li><span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">Having skills in using multimedia and internet resources are advantage</span></span></span></li>\n</ul>\n\n<p><br>\n<span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\"><span style=\"font-family:Lucida Sans Unicode,Lucida Grande,sans-serif;\">If you feel that you can meet the qualification and up for the challenge, please send your complete resume and current color photograph to info@kidsrepublic.sch.id</span></span></span></p>',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','page','text',NULL,'default',25,'left-sidebar','latest-news',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-12-08 18:01:06','2019-12-