-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; word-spacing: 0px;\"><br>\n<span style=\"color:#333333;\"><span style=\"font-size:20px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 115%;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">Kids Republic provides a wide range of club activities/ extracurricular to support our student’s motoric and socio-emotional developments. These activities are designed to meet our student’s talents and hobbies in the field of non-academics but are equal in importance as part of their educations. In older classes (4 – 6 years old), students are compulsory to join club activities as a part of our holistic curriculum. Whereas it is optional for our younger students (2 – 4 years old).</span></span></span></span></p>\n&nbsp;',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','page','text',NULL,'column-two-with-carousel',20,'left-sidebar','latest-news',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-12-15 10:37:06','2019-12-15 10:50:31'),(64,'flyer','Flyer','Admission Primary School','Kids Republic',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','page','text',NULL,'column-two-with-carousel',24,'left-sidebar','latest-news',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-12-15 11:32:01','2019-12-26 05:49:14'),(65,'parent-1','Parent','About Us','Testimonial',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','page','component','testimoni-component','default',27,'left-sidebar','latest-news',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-12-15 11:44:16','2019-12-15 11:44:16'),(77,'title','title','heading title','last title',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'1578900860_5e1c1d7c840b9.jpeg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','page','component','teacher-component','column-two-with-slider',7,'left-sidebar','latest-news',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2020-01-13 00:34:20','2020-01-13 00:35:33'),(81,'program-baru','Program Baru',NULL,'Subtitlenya',NULL,'hahaha',NULL,NULL,'1579191106_5e208b42060e6.jpeg',300,200,0,0,0,0,'left','open','publish','program',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2020-01-16 09:11:46','2020-01-16 18:27:06'),(89,'kids-republic-unicorn-party','Kids Republic Unicorn Party',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Who doesn\'t love Unicorn?<br />\n<br />\nThis December, Kids Republic will have a Unicorn Party at Unicorn Land, Main Atrium Cipinang Indah Mall.<br />\n<br />\nYou can join us and participate in:<br />\n<br />\na. Parenting Talkshow, \"Multiple Intelligence: Understanding Your Child\'s Learning Style\" with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/aninda143/\">@aninda143</a><br />\n<br />\nb. Show and Exhibition (Ballet Performance, Kids Dance and Flashmob)<br />\n<br />\nc. Baby and Kids Competitions (Baby Crawling, Feeding the Unicorns, Unicorn Cake Decorating, Unicorn Fashion Show)<br />\n<br />\nSave the date: Sunday, 8 December 2019 at 11 am until 5 pm.<br />\n<br />\nClick link&nbsp;for RSVP: bit.ly/kidsunicornparty<br />\n<br />\nOr text us 0821 2007 7600</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'WhatsApp Image 2019-11-20 at 14.45.51-96604.jpeg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','event',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Main Atrium Cipinang Indah Mall',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-11-22 02:02:29','2019-11-22 02:02:29'),(90,'children-s-day-celebration','Children\'s Day Celebration',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>This November, Kids Republic celebrates one of the most important day of the year. We celebrate International Children’s Day. This year, we celebrate it a little more differently. Our theme for this year is “Education Equality for Children of Indonesia”. We will have a charity project for our little friends at PAUD Harapan Bunda, that doesn’t have educational tools and materials in their school.<br />\n<br />\nThe students will be 100% involved in this project. All parents and other community at school will be invited on this day. On the Market Day, we will use Kids Republic’s currency. To buy the product, you have to exchange your money at the “Money Exchange Booth” at Admission Office starting Wednesday, 19 November 2019 until the D-Day or until the KR Money that the school has prepared is sold out. The rate is Rp 10.000,- for 10 KR. The product’s price will be around 50 KR.<br />\n<br />\nHow the parents can participate?<br />\nThe parents can participate by buying or donating. On the D-Day, we will also open “Donation Booth”, everyone can donate their money and stuffs at the booth. The parents are also allowed to donate money or raw materials for the class, to be made into the product that the students are going to sell. All the revenue will be 100% donated to PAUD Harapan Bunda.<br />\n<br />\nWe really hope this event will be meaningful, not only to our children, but also to our little friends at PAUD Harapan Bunda, and to ourselves. We also hope this event can help the students to sharpen their socio-emotional skill and empathy, and encourage them to contribute in helping others in larger and boarder perspectives.</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'75281144_433553800928429_8992651205901742236_n-66694.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','event',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'Nusa Indah Intersection',NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-11-29 02:26:14','2019-11-29 02:30:34'),(91,'mother-s-day-celebration','Mother\'s Day Celebration',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Mom, thank you for giving me life.. Please come to see what I am going to present you at school on Thursday, 19 December 2019.<br />\n<br />\nMinister &amp; President at 08.00 - 10.30<br />\nMayor &amp; Governor at 10.00 - 12.30<br />\n<br />\nI\'ll see you there!<br />\n<br />\nWishing you a lovely Mother\'s Day ?</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'backdrop-mothers-day-58271.png',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','event',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,N