>\n',NULL,NULL,'WhatsApp Image 2018-11-19 at 16.16.00 (1)-96358.jpeg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2018-11-19 09:18:48','2018-11-19 09:18:48'),(111,'childrens-day-market-day-charity-for-palu-donggala','Childrens Day & Market Day \'Charity for Palu & Donggala\'',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Alhamdulillah hari ini Kids Republic bersama dengan&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/psg.kidsrepublic/\">@psg.kidsrepublic</a>telah menyerahkan hasil donasi yang terkumpul pada acara Market Day Jumat lalu. Seluruh uang dan barang barang yang terkumpul langsung disalurkan kepada&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/actforhumanity/\">@actforhumanity</a>&nbsp;untuk saudara kita yang terkena bencana gempa dan tsunami di Palu dan Donggala.<br />\n<br />\nSekali lagi kami ucapkan terima kasih kepada seluruh pihak yang telah berpartisipasi.</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'market day-73827.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2018-12-25 16:41:21','2018-12-25 16:42:19'),(112,'psg-comittee-2018-2019','PSG Comittee 2018/2019',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Hari ini, Selasa, 27 November 2018, telah dilakukan serah terima jabatan dari kepengurusan PSG 2017/ 2018 ke kepengurusan PSG 2018/ 2019.<br />\n.<br />\nKami (guru-guru dan staff, manajemen) dari sekolah mengucapkan terima kasih banyak kepada pengurus PSG 2017/ 2018 atas dedikasinya selama 1 tahun 1 bulan.<br />\n.<br />\nWe deeply appreciate all your service and contribution to the school, especially the love and attention to our teachers ????<br />\n.<br />\nUntuk kepengurusan PSG 2018/ 2019, perwakilan orangtua telah menyepakati untuk menunjuk Mommy Samara (Ibu Lintang) sebagai Ketua PSG 2018/ 2019<br />\n.<br />\nMudah-mudahan Kids Republic parents selalu kompak, dan PSG bisa memfasilitasi kebutuhan Mommy &amp; Daddy semua.<br />\n.<br />\nDan insya Allah mudah-mudahan sekolah bisa beriringan dengan&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/psg.kidsrepublic/\">@psg.kidsrepublic</a>menjadi wadah positif bagi para orangtua, demi pendidikan terbaik untuk anak-anak :) Have a great day!<br />\n.</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'psg 2018 2019-55327.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2018-12-25 16:44:50','2018-12-25 16:44:50'),(113,'earthquake-drill','Earthquake Drill',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Today, everyone at Kids Republic School were doing earthquake drill.<br />\n<br />\nThe students, teachers, coaches and staff were trained to drop, cover and hold for 1 minute when hearing the earthquake alarm.<br />\n<br />\nAfter 1 minute passed, everyone was lining up one by one (led by 1 teacher at the front, and one at the back) and was directed to the Assembly Point.<br />\n<br />\nClass teachers checked if the students were already complete, and the principal checked if all the classes (students and teachers) were already complete and safe.<br />\n<br />\nOperational Team and HRD were responsible to check if all staff were already complete. Thank you for Operational Team who has organized this drill for us at school.<br />\n<br />\nThis drill will be held frequently as a cautious act, just in case anything happen.<br />\n<br />\nLet\'s pray that God will protect us from any harm and disaster.</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'earth quake-22484.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2018-12-25 16:46:14','2018-12-25 16:46:14'),(114,'vaksin-difteri','Vaksin Difteri',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>DPT adalah singkatan dari difteri, pertusis, dan tetanus. Imunisasi DPT adalah salah satu vaksinasi yang wajib diberikan kepada balita.<br />\n<br />\nPenyakit difteri, pertusis, dan tetanus adalah tiga penyakit berbeda yang masing-masing memiliki risiko tinggi dan bahkan bisa menyebabkan kematian. Ketiga penyakit ini adalah penyakit serius yang disebabkan oleh bakteri. Oleh karena itu, pemberian imunisasi DPT sebaiknya tidak dilewatkan.<br />\n<br />\nKids Republic School bekerjasama dengen Puskesmas Cipinang Muara, Jarinegara, mengadakan Vaksin Difteri Tahap 3 kepada seluruh anak anak yang terdata belum melakukan vaksin jenis ini.<br />\n<br />\nGood Job Friends!</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'47342442_1995293717182836_3434031064178229248_n-68586.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2018-12-25 16:47:29','2018-12-25 16:47:29'),(115,'open-house-kids-republic-cipinang','Open House Kids Republic Cipinang',NULL,NULL,NULL,'Dear Parents,<br />\n<br />\nThankyou for coming to our school.<br />\nHope you all enjoy our presentation.<br />\n<br />\n:)',NULL,NULL,'48387597_2011866875525520_5267942143489474560_n-34538.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2018-12-25 16:52:40','2018-12-25 16:52:40'),(116,'montessori-workshop','Montessori Workshop',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Dear Parents,<br />\n<br />\nThankyou for coming to our school.<br />\nHope you all enjoy our presentation.<br />\n<br />\n:)<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'48314202_2011867142192160_6516667064046845952_n-59648.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2018-12-25 16:53:32','2018-12-25 16:53:32'),(117,'our-principal-in-parent-thing-ktv','Our Principal in Parent Thing KTV',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Terimakasih KTV telah mengundang kami untuk berbagi ilmu mengenai ‘Metode Montessori untuk Pendidikan Anak Usia Dini’ dalam program Parent Things. Taping ini akan tayang tanggal 28 Desember 2018 pukul 13.00 siang hanya 