lic Festival Day 3 \"Run For The Earth 3k\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Finally, Kids Republic Festival Day 3 Run For The Earth! Luar biasa sekali antusiasme dari siswa siswi serta orang tua murid yang ikut dalam kegiatan ini.&nbsp;<br />\nSelain lari pagi, kegiatan ini juga merupakan salah satu wujud nyata bahwa Kids Republic Family ikut andil dalam campaign go green dan mencintai bumi.&nbsp;<br />\nSelain itu, dalam rangka menyambut hari buku Internasional&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/psg.kidsrepublic/\">@psg.kidsrepublic</a>&nbsp;bekerjasama dengan&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/1001buku/\">@1001buku</a>&nbsp;mengadakan children books donation.&nbsp;<br />\nTerimakasih juga kami ucapkan untuk&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/orami_id/\">@orami_id</a>&nbsp;yang telah mensupport event ini.&nbsp;<br />\nSekali lagi, terimakasih banyak untuk semua pihak yang ikut berpartisipasi dalam rangkaian acara Kids Republic Festival 2019 ini. Semoga kegiatan ini bermanfaat. Sampai jumpa di Kids Republic Festival tahun depan.&nbsp;<br />\nHave a nice weekend friends</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'IMG_8258.JPG',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-05-17 07:05:43','2019-05-17 07:06:08'),(137,'kids-republic-graduation-year-end-concert-2019','Kids Republic Graduation & Year End Concert 2019',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Today is your day. You\'re off to Great Places! You\'re off and away!<br />\n<br />\nYou have brains in your head. You have feet in your shoes. You can steer yourself&nbsp;any direction you choose. You\'re on your own. And you know what you know.<br />\n<br />\nAnd YOU are the guy who\'ll decide where to go.<br />\n<br />\nBig thanks to everyone who takes part and participate in this event:<br />\n- Yayasan Batin Cahaya Bangsa (Kids Republic)<br />\n-&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/purebaby.indonesia/\">@purebaby.indonesia</a><br />\n-&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/halodoc/\">@halodoc</a><br />\n-&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sammarie_basra/\">@sammarie_basra</a><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'12-81721.png',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-07-25 14:03:12','2019-07-25 14:03:12'),(138,'kids-republic-graduation-year-end-concert-2019-1','Kids Republic Graduation & Year End Concert 2019',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>It\'s opener there in the wide open air. Out there things can happen, and frequently do to people as brainy and footsy as you. And then things start to happen, don\'t worry. Don\'t stew. Just go right along. You\'ll start happening too.<br />\n<br />\nOH! THE PLACES YOU\'LL GO!<br />\n<br />\nBig thanks to everyone who takes part and participate in this event:<br />\n- Yayasan Batin Cahaya Bangsa (Kids Republic)<br />\n-&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/purebaby.indonesia/\">@purebaby.indonesia</a><br />\n-&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/halodoc/\">@halodoc</a><br />\n-&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sammarie_basra/\">@sammarie_basra</a><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'19-30034.png',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-07-25 14:04:09','2019-07-25 14:04:09'),(139,'kids-republic-graduation-year-end-concert','Kids Republic Graduation & Year End Concert',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>\"We keep moving forward, opening new doors and doing new things, because we\'re curious,and curiosity keeps leading us down new paths.” - Walt Disney<br />\n<br />\nBig thanks to everyone who takes part and participate in this event:<br />\n- Yayasan Batin Cahaya Bangsa (Kids Republic)<br />\n-&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/purebaby.indonesia/\">@purebaby.indonesia</a><br />\n-&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/halodoc/\">@halodoc</a><br />\n-&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/sammarie_basra/\">@sammarie_basra</a></p>\n',NULL,NULL,'35-26587.png',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-07-25 14:05:12','2019-07-25 14:05:12'),(140,'holiday-program-dino-science-camp','Holiday Program \"Dino Science Camp\"',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Dreaming to be a scientist? Realise it through our Science Camp activities!<br />\n<br />\nDino Science Camp Day 1 - Kids Republic and Alfa and Friends are on an adventure on a hovercraft. Suddenly they are carried aloft by twister of the powerful tornado.<br />\n<br />\nDino Science Camp Day 2 - They crash land in the dark cave. They turn on their LED Headlamps. Light from headlamp brighten the cave and they see creepy Worms everywhere!<br />\n<time datetime=\"2019-07-09T13:24:24.000Z\" title=\"9 Juli 2019\">2 ming</time><br />\n<br />\nDino Science Camp Day 3 - Ollie accidently kick something and saw a Giant Egg. They put on their 3D Glasses and realise that they are in the World of Dinosaurs!<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Dino Science Camp Day 4 - They discover Fossils that might belong to the dinosaurs. The ground shake as they hear T-Rex\'s roar. They run away from chasing Dinosaurs and fall down a clift.<br />\n<br />\nDino Science Camp Day 5 - They will make a Zoetrope 3D Puzzle. They wake up and realise it\'s just a dream. The egg in their hand cracks and it\'s a baby Dinosaurs!<br />\n<br />\nDino Science Camp Day 6 - They will come to visit the Taman Legenda Keong Emas Museum to experience the history of Dinosaurs.</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'110719b-84097.png',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-07-25 14:08:18','2019-07-25 14:08:18'),(141,'first-day-of-school-cipinang','First Day Of School Cipinang',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>First day of school at Kids Republic Cipinang.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nSetelah libur&nbsp;panjang akhir tahun ajaran, akhirnya sampailah kita pada hari pertama masuk sekolah. Semua anak sangat bersemangat untuk kembali ke sekolah! Sungguh menyenangkan melihat canda tawa dan senyuman teman-teman kecil ini di sekolah. Welcome back to school friends! Let\'s make some fun at Kids Republic School!</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'IMG_7847-36478.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-08-21 03:21:00','2019-08-21 03:21:00'),(142,'first-day-of-school-at-kids-republic-galaxy','First day of school at Kids Republic Galaxy.',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>First day of school at Kids Republic Galaxy.&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nSetelah libur&nbsp;panjang akhir tahun ajaran, akhirnya sampailah kita pada hari pertama masuk sekolah. Semua anak sangat bersemangat untuk kembali ke sekolah! Sungguh menyenangkan melihat canda tawa dan senyuman teman-teman kecil ini di sekolah. Welcome back to school friends! Let\'s make some fun at Kids Republic School!</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'67580052_239036947052458_4712318355868553753_n-98143.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-08-21 03:34:15','2019-08-21 03:34:15'),(143,'indonesia-independence-day-celebration','Indonesia Independence Day Celebration',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>This year’s theme of Indonesia Independence Day Celebration at Kids Republic School is “Focus on Collaboration, Instead of Competition.\" All the games were played by students, parents, and staff as well, are all about teamwork and collaboration.<br />\n<br />\nWe believe that everyone is a champion as long as they give their best effort and be the best version of themselves.<br />\n<br />\nWe believe that this is the era where to achieve greatness is to do things together, hand in hand.<br />\n<br />\nThat it\'s not