nts day celebration kali ini, Kids Republic Cipinang kedatangan tamu istimewa lho.. Yap our beloved Grandpa and Grandma! Terima kasih atas kedatangannya Grandpa and Grandma, senang sekali bisa seharian berkegiatan di sekolah bersama. I love you Grandpa and Grandma!</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'200919-34355.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-09-20 04:29:06','2019-09-20 04:29:06'),(147,'kids-republic-cipinang-mayor-and-governor-class-fieldtrip-to-kuntum-farmfield','Kids Republic Cipinang Mayor and Governor Class fieldtrip to Kuntum Farmfield',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Kids Republic Cipinang Mayor and Governor Class fieldtrip to Kuntum Farmfield. We are learn and play with the plants and animals there!</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'171019-32101.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-10-22 12:35:35','2019-10-22 12:35:35'),(148,'minister-president-class-fieldtrip-to-pelita-desa-outbound-ciseeng','Minister & President Class fieldtrip to Pelita Desa Outbound Ciseeng',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Minister &amp; President Class fieldtrip to Pelita Desa Outbound Ciseeng. Thank you for the great memories friends!</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'221019b-97691.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-11-12 07:46:52','2019-11-12 07:46:52'),(149,'student-observation-parents-interview-kids-republic-primary-school-tier-1','Student Observation & Parents Interview Kids Republic Primary School Tier 1',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Student Observation &amp; Parents Interview Kids Republic Primary School Tier 1.<br />\nAnd get ready for The 2nd Tier of Registration Kids Republic Primary School on this November!</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'041119-19209.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-11-12 07:48:00','2019-11-12 07:48:00'),(150,'kids-republic-children-s-day','Kids Republic Children\'s Day',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Thank you for the enthusiasm Mom &amp; Dad also the Kiddos. Yesterday\'s Children\'s Day was awesome. Starting from the student parade, market day, and the last but not least the handprints on paper with Paud Harapan Bunda\'s student. All the revenue from Market Day, will be 100% donated to PAUD Harapan Bunda.<br />\n<br />\nWe really hope this event will be meaningful, not only to our children, but also to our little friends at PAUD Harapan Bunda, and to ourselves. We also hope this event can help the students to sharpen their socio-emotional skill and empathy, and encourage them to contribute in helping others in larger and boarder perspectives.</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'WhatsApp Image 2019-11-28 at 14.28.22-82494.jpeg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-11-29 02:33:33','2019-11-29 02:33:33'),(151,'teachers-day-celebration','Teachers Day Celebration',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Parents Support Group, perwakilan Mommy &amp; Daddy serta teman-teman kecil Kids Republic School Cipinang dan Galaxy mengadakan acara Teachers Day Celebration&nbsp;untuk Miss &amp; Coaches. Acara ini rutin dilakukan setiap tahunnya, dalam rangka apresiasi kepada seluruh guru-guru Kids Republic School.<br />\n<br />\nTerima kasih banyak Mommy &amp; Daddy atas kepercayaan yang sangat besar yang diberikan kepada kami untuk bersama sama menciptakan generasi generasi penerus bangsa yang hebat</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'WhatsApp Image 2019-12-13 at 16.32.34 (1).jpeg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-12-26 07:31:54','2019-12-26 07:34:58'),(152,'kids-republic-unicorn-party-1','Kids Republic Unicorn Party',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Terima kasih untuk semua yang telah hadir ikut berbagi keseruan dan meramaikan acara ini. Meskipun berlangsung hampir seharian, namun antusiasme tetap tinggi hingga acara berakhir.<br />\n<br />\nDibuka dengan peformance cantik dari teman-teman ballerina dari Kids Republic Ballet Dance x&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/rafadance_id/\">@rafadance_id</a>, dilanjutkan dengan Parenting Talkshow bersama dengan Ms.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/rakhmiramdhani/\">@rakhmiramdhani</a>&nbsp;dan Mrs.&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/aninda143/\">@aninda143</a>&nbsp;mengenai \"Multiple Intelligence: Understanding Your Child\'s Learning Style\" yang juga berlangsung seru dan menarik.<br />\n<br />\nLalu keseruan acara dilanjutkan dengan penampilan dari teman-teman Little Dance dan Kids Dance by Kids Republic&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/gymnasticacademy_/\">@gymnasticacademy_</a>&nbsp;dan Unicorn-Themed Competition yang terdiri dari berbagai lomba dari usia 6 bulan hingga usia 6 tahun, yaitu: Crawling Competition, Feeding The Unicorn, Unicorn Cake Decoration dan Unicorn Fashion Show.<br />\n<br />\nGreat job, friends! See you at Kids Republic next events!<br />\n<br />\nThank you too for the support:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/mallcipinangindah/\">@mallcipinangindah</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/momnjogalaxy/\">@momnjogalaxy</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/momnjokalimalang/\">@momnjokalimalang</a></p>\n',NULL,NULL,'WhatsApp Image 2019-12-08 at 18.45.29-68623.jpeg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-12-26 07:35:54','2019-12-26 07:35:54'),(153,'mother-s-day-celebration-1','Mother\'s Day Celebration',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Dear Beloved Mommies,<br />\nYou always clean the fingerprints<br />\nI leave upon the wall<br />\nI seem to make a mess of things,<br />\nbecause I was so small<br />\nThe years will pass so quickly, I’ll soon be grown like you<br />\nAnd all my little fingerprints, will surely fade from view<br />\nSo here is a special fingerprint, a memory that is true<br />\nSo you’ll recall the very day, I made it just for you!<br />\n<br />\nThank you for coming. Happy Mother\'s Day. I love you mom</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'WhatsApp Image 2019-12-19 at 18.15.41-45597.jpeg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-12-26 07:36:52','2019-12-26 07:36:52'),(154,'end-of-year-potluck','End of Year Potluck',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>End of year potluck. This year is awesome, let’s make more good memories at 2020! See you next year friends!</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'WhatsApp Image 2019-12-20 at 17.34.14-68014.jpeg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','artikel',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-12-26 07:38:47','2019-12-26 07:38:47'),(155,'kids-republic-s-ballet-open-trial-forpublic-every-saturday','Kids Republic\'s Ballet Open Trial forPublic Every Saturday',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Good News!<br />\n<br />\nKids Republic Gymnastic Academy Galaxy Incollaboration with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.instagram.com/rafadance_id/\">@rafadance_id</a>present: Ballet Class Open Trial For Public at Kids Republic Galaxy.<br />\n<br />\nWe\'re open Ballet Class for:<br />\n1. Ballet Pre-School (3 - 4,5 Years)<br />\n2. Ballet Pre-Primary (4,5 - 6 Years)<br />\n<br />\nRegistration today, and get the special price for early bird!<br />\n<br />\nDon\'t missed this good opportunity to enroll your kids since our seats are now limited! Special for those that booked in December will get a Free Registration Fee and 50% discount for tuition fee.&nbsp;<br />\nWan\'t to know about our Ballet Class program? Come and Join us at Ballet Class Open Trial, and get special price!<br />\n<br />\nFor RSVP please WA 0821 1300 0041<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'ballet galaxy open trial every saturday-79234.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','promo',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2018-12-25 16:57:01','2018-12-25 16:57:01'),(156,'kids-republic-open-franchise','Kids Republic Open Franchise',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Kids Republic School Open Franchise! Want to open play school and looking for low investment Montessori Pre School &amp; Kindergarten franchise? Come and Join with Kids Republic School \"Montessori &amp; Gymnastic Academy\". Contact Us: 0821 200 77 600</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'WhatsApp Image 2019-02-19 at 17.56.53.jpeg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','promo',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-02-11 02:00:00','2019-02-19 11:39:00'),(157,'kids-republic-qur-an-learning-course','Kids Republic Qur\'an Learning Course',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Dear Parents,<br />\n<br />\nTahu gak sih, mengapa Ilmu Agama Sangat Penting?<br />\n<br />\nSama halnya dengan ilmu pelajaran lain di sekolah, ilmu agama selalu mengedepankan kebaikan dan memberi manfaat yang luar biasa bagi kecerdasan anak. Melalui agama, anak bisa mengenal berbagai kebaikan dari yang paling dasar hingga yang paling tinggi tingkatannya.<br />\n<br />\nMelalui ilmu agama, anak-anak akan menjaga diri dan menjauhkan diri dari hal-hal yang dilarang norma masyarakat atau pun agama.<br />\n<br />\nJadi apakah moms and dads masih ragu untuk menanamkan ilmu agama sejak dini?<br />\n<strong>Yuk daftarkan si kecil di Kids Republic Haqiqi&nbsp;Qur’an Learning Class</strong>. Kuota terbatas lho moms.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Extracurricular ini terbuka untuk publik!</strong><br />\n<br />\nFor further information,&nbsp;<strong>please call<br />\nKids Republic Cipinang: 0821 200 77 600</strong><br />\n<strong>Kids Republic Galaxy: 0813 888 333 43</strong><br />\n<br />\nWarm Regards,<br />\n<strong>Kids Republic Team</strong></p>\n',NULL,NULL,'FLYER-QURAN-LEARNING.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','promo',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-07-25 09:22:27','2019-12-27 02:15:04'),(158,'kids-republic-training-center','Kids Republic Training Center',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p><strong>DO YOU WANT TO BE A MONTESSORIAN?</strong><br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nLet\'s join us at&nbsp;<strong>Kids Republic Training Center.</strong><br />\nJoin&nbsp;<strong>\'full package\'</strong>&nbsp;and get the<strong>&nbsp;special price</strong>&nbsp;and also bonus 2 session of class:<br />\nart &amp; craft, science class, cooking &amp;&nbsp;food preparation, and first aid short training.<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Let\'s join us today!</strong><br />\nMore info please call 021 29827245 | 0821 200 77 600<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\nWarm Regards,<br />\n<strong>Kids Republic Team</strong></p>\n',NULL,NULL,'montessori-training-center.png',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','promo',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-07-25 11:03:14','2019-07-25 11:04:33'),(159,'extracurricular-kids-republic-cipinang-open-for-public','Extracurricular Kids Republic Cipinang Open For Public',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p><strong>Apakah Pendidikan Formal Saja Cukup?&nbsp;</strong></p>\n\n<p>Moms, selain pendidikan formal, aktifitas non akademik pun suatu hal yang wajib dilakukan oleh Si Kecil yaa. Kids Republic,&nbsp;menyediakan berbagai kegiatan untuk mendukung perkembangan motorik dan sosial-emosional. Kegiatan-kegiatan ini dirancang untuk memenuhi bakat dan hobi siswa kami di bidang non-akademik,tetapi sama pentingnya sebagai bagian dari pendidikan mereka.<br />\n<br />\nYuk kenali, ada Extracurricular Activity apa saja&nbsp;di Kids Republic School Cipinang dan Galaxy!</p>\n\n<p>Extracurricular Activity&nbsp;ini&nbsp;<strong>terbuka untuk umum</strong>&nbsp;dengan ketentuan usia 2,5 - 6 tahun.<br />\n<br />\nWhat are you waiting for, let\'s register your child now!<br />\n<strong>Seats are limited!</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>More info please WA:</strong><br />\nKids Republic Cipinang: 0821 200 77 600<br />\nKids Republic Galaxy: 0813 888 333 43<br />\n<br />\nWarm Regards,<br />\n<strong>Kids Republic Team</strong></p>\n',NULL,NULL,'PROMO-EXCUL-CIPINANG-89997.png',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','promo',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-08-21 05:01:12','2019-08-21 05:01:12'),(160,'extracurricular-kids-republic-galaxy-open-for-public','Extracurricular Kids Republic Galaxy Open For Public',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Moms, selain pendidikan formal, aktifitas non akademik pun suatu hal yang wajib dilakukan oleh Si Kecil yaa. Kids Republic,&nbsp;menyediakan berbagai kegiatan untuk mendukung perkembangan motorik dan sosial-emosional. Kegiatan-kegiatan ini dirancang untuk memenuhi bakat dan hobi siswa kami di bidang non-akademik,tetapi sama pentingnya sebagai bagian dari pendidikan mereka.<br />\n<br />\nYuk kenali, ada Extracurricular Activity apa saja&nbsp;di Kids Republic School Cipinang dan Galaxy!</p>\n\n<p>Extracurricular Activity&nbsp;ini&nbsp;<strong>terbuka untuk umum</strong>&nbsp;dengan ketentuan usia 2,5 - 6 tahun.<br />\n<br />\nWhat are you waiting for, let\'s register your child now!<br />\n<strong>Seats are limited!</strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong>More info please WA:</strong><br />\nKids Republic Cipinang: 0821 200 77 600<br />\nKids Republic Galaxy: 0813 888 333 43<br />\n<br />\nWarm Regards,<br />\n<strong>Kids Republic Team</strong></p>\n',NULL,NULL,'PROMO-EXCUL-GALAXY-39844.png',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','promo',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-08-21 05:05:12','2019-08-21 05:05:12'),(161,'first-15-students-enrolled-free-extracurricular-gymnastic-academy','First 15 students enrolled FREE EXTRACURRICULAR GYMNASTIC ACADEMY',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>GOOD NEWS!!! First 15 students enrolled at Kids Republic Primary School academic year of 2020/2021, get FREE EXTRACURRICULAR GYMNASTIC ACADEMY for August 2020 - June 2021!<br />\n<br />\nKids Republic Primary School Already Open Enrollment for Academic Year of 2020/2021 for Tier 1!<br />\n<br />\nPlease take a note the Tier 1 Admission Procedure!<br />\nClick link below for Online Registration:<br />\nbit.ly/krforminquiry<br />\nOr click link on bio!<br />\n<br />\nMore info please WA 0821 200 77 600<br />\nCS Availabe Mon - Fri from 08.00 AM - 15.00 PM</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'70199440_155897768946863_4167316545609335621_n-44641.jpg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','promo',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-10-22 12:33:24','2019-10-22 12:33:24'),(162,'open-enrollment-gymnastic-academy','Open Enrollment Gymnastic Academy',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Kids Republic Gymnastic program is a sports club designed for baby, kids, and teenagers aged 6 months to 14 years old.<br />\nWith our child friendly facility, we create a fun way for children to exercise using our specialized Leaders Curriculum© to bring out the best from our little ones.<br />\nMaximal learning (windows of opportunity) happens especially in the golden age (0 - 5 years), meaning you will see your little ones progress remarkably with appropriate stimulation physically, academically, socially and morally as well. Leaders Curriculum© will promote the following skills.<br />\n<br />\nOur activities promote team-building, communication skills, instil values and enable children to be physically fit.<br />\nWe believe that a healthy body equals a healthy mind.<br />\n- Stimulate Your Senses: Sensorial exploration, using manipulative materials, enables children to maximize their creative potential.<br />\n- Move Your Body: Rhythmic dancing helps our little ones to develop listening skills, love for music and whole body awareness. Music and movement are great for their emotional wellbeing.<br />\n- Tumble &amp; Crawl: It utilizes physical activities to burn energy while developing body coordination, balance, spatial awareness and gross motor skills. It also helps our little ones to stay fit!<br />\n- Leaders Maximizers: Activities are designed to teach leadership skills, teamwork, social skills, confidence and good moral values. These skills will enable our little ones to stay fit!<br />\n<br />\nJoin us today!<br />\n<br />\nMore info:<br />\nGymnastic Academy Cipinang 0821 200 77 600<br />\nGymnastic Academy Galaxy 0813 888 333 43<br />\nemail: info@kidsrepublic.sch.id</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'WhatsApp Image 2019-12-10 at 11.00.15-15809.jpeg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','promo',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-12-26 07:19:57','2019-12-26 07:19:57'),(163,'open-enrollment-preschool-kindergarten','Open Enrollment Preschool & Kindergarten',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>Kids Republic adopts National Curriculum of Indonesia and applies it in almost all aspect of our subjects. We teach Indonesian language weekly, we instil moral &amp; religion values in and after classes. Our students will be ready to enter either national or international choice of school.<br />\n<br />\nEach month, all classes in Kids Republic will be using different themes. Theme is an effective method for early childhood students by conducting experiments and direct study to foster student’s creativity and imagination. School will provide different theme for each month, such as: Under the Sea, Space, Farm, Community Helpers and many more. Not only children will learn general ideas from their lesson plan but they will get additional information through in depth studies such as thematic.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<b>Learning Methodologies</b></p>\n\n<ul>\n	<li>Group Presentation</li>\n	<li>Individual Presentation</li>\n	<li>Experiment</li>\n	<li>Moving Class</li>\n	<li>Edu – Trip</li>\n	<li>Outside the class observation</li>\n	<li>Performance</li>\n	<li>Assembly</li>\n	<li>Class Chores</li>\n	<li>Group Projects</li>\n	<li>Individual Projects</li>\n</ul>\nJoin us today!<br />\n<br />\nMore info:<br />\nGymnastic Academy Cipinang 0821 200 77 600<br />\nGymnastic Academy Galaxy 0813 888 333 43<br />\nEmail: info@kidsrepublic.sch.id',NULL,NULL,'WhatsApp Image 2019-12-10 at 11.00.15 (1)-53341.jpeg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','promo',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-12-26 07:27:15','2019-12-26 07:27:15'),(164,'open-enrollment-kids-republic-primary-school','Open Enrollment Kids Republic Primary School',NULL,NULL,NULL,'<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Kids Republic Primary School Open Enrollment for Academic Year of 2020/2021 for Tier 2!<br />\n<br />\nPlease take a note the Tier 2 Admission Procedure!<br />\nKindly click link below for Online Registration:<br />\nbit.ly/krforminquiry<br />\n<br />\nMore info please WA 0821 200 77 600<br />\nCS Availabe Mon - Fri from 08.00 AM - 15.00 PM<br />\n<br />\nSee you! :)</p>\n',NULL,NULL,'WhatsApp Image 2019-12-10 at 11.00.15 (2)-46951.jpeg',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,'open','publish','promo',NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,NULL,1,NULL,NULL,NULL,'2019-12-26 07:28:43','2019-12-26 07:28:43');
